She transformed into bot mode and ran over to Striker.  She tried to 
drag him over band back into the ark.  She opened her link,"IF there 
are any Maximald in the ARK, we could use your help out here."
She said as she kept trying to drag Striker inside.  She kept her 
guard up incase they attacked her while trying to save Striker.
